latestIgtvVideos.title: Monochrome barbie look
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Monochrome look #MyGlammIsMonochromatic

I have taken monochrome look weekly challenge. It was a lot of fun for me to take this creative challenge with MyGlamm. I have created this look with variants of single Pink colour across my eyes, lips and cheeks and products are from MYGLAMM. I have used one lipstick for making this beautiful Pink eyeshadow and another for contouring. You can also create this simple look within your budget like me. Check below the products name I have used in this look
Products used:
Pink eyeshadow+lipstick with MyGlamm LIT liquid matte lipstick in shade "15 Cuffing"
Eyeliner+eyebrows with MyGlamm jet set eyes kajal and eyeliner in shade NOIR
Foundation+eyebase with MyGlamm clean beauty argan oil BB Foundation stick in shade OAK
Contour with MyGlamm perfect curves matte lip crayon in shade "Terra"
Blush with MyGlamm K.Play flavoured blush in shade "Juicy strawberry"
Highlighter with MyGlamm K.Play flavoured highlighter in shade "Pink Rose"

#MyGlammXO #MyGlammXOBeautyCreator @myglammxo_beautycreator @plixxo @popxobeauty @myglamm
